Package: rctbayespower
Title: Bayesian Power Analysis for Randomized Controlled Trials
Version: 0.1.0
Description: Provides tools for conducting Bayesian power analysis for randomized controlled trials (RCTs) using 'brms' and Stan. The package enables simulation-based power analysis with flexible threshold-based decision criteria, estimation of power curves, and determination of optimal sample sizes. Supports continuous, binary, and count outcomes with custom model formulas, prior specifications, and parallel processing capabilities.
Author: Matthias Kloft [aut, cre, cph] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1845-6957>)
Maintainer: Matthias Kloft <kloft@uni-marburg.de>
